\section*{Introduction}

 A system in which data of Patient, data of donor, data of blood bank would be saved and will be interrelation with each other

\section*{Objectives}
\begin{itemize}
\begin{itemize}
\item  Create an user-friendly interface.
\item  Create registration and login system for users.
\item  Create a database containing user and their blood groups.
\item  Create tables containing all information about patient and donor.
\end{itemize}
\end{itemize}

\section*{Target}
\begin{itemize}
\begin{itemize}
\item  People who in need of blood.
\item  People who want to donate their blood.
\end{itemize}
\end{itemize}

\section*{Value Proposition}
Across Bangladesh, every day there remains an urgent need for all types of blood groups. Especially donors with rare blood groups such as O Negative , B Negative and A Negative are in high demand.Our timely response is essential to the supply of healthy blood for the massive daily demand we face.

\section*{Features}
\begin{itemize}
\begin{itemize}
\item  Anyone can search for \textbf{blood} at anytime from anywhere.
\item  Registered user can chat with each other.
\item  Users can pin their location on Map. \\
\textit{*(More features will be added if possible)}
\end{itemize}
\end{itemize}

\section*{Tools and Resources}
